Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,=================text===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 難道被誰做了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快放開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那為什麼要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好溫柔 真的在擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不過已經忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,和涼在一起很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,倉谷 真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要用到報告說但是完全寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.66,0:00:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便地吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,說了狠話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,涼一直在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我已經喜歡上涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,倉谷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,給你 暖的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,來見朋友 碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這個多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,請你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是和男朋友吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小南最近看起來很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,想著是不是有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡小南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 這樣太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小南最近變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說不擅長和男生講話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是為此努力著的身影好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,從很久以前就喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,能和我交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,已經和那個人交往了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且肯定已經被討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就算小南現在不喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,能先試著和我交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,候補男朋友怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,等到靜歌的心意明確為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在你身邊 不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道這樣讓你等是很狡猾的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是已經察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不被引導
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好地把我的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我不能和穀倉交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你明確地告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,心情舒暢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼學校再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,靜歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 涼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛還不是女裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是男生的樣子的話你可能不願意見我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,涼在生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不道歉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛你說有喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這表情要給別人看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 你聽到剛才的話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是說你有喜歡的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然隨靜歌忍著當候補男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是既然如此就不需要忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰 一個學校的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好害怕
